topics.body:
!http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20120401090725/kamenrider/images/b/b9/N-Daguva-Zeba-Human.jpg!
Jogu, zagododo-zoro.

Goze bo barage za N-Daguva-Zeba. Goze zogora gedaji gajido shibo bosazubi sagiza. Bobobu zasabu bogibu be Rinto-zoro ga. Bosogi zogida bodoza gasuboba, jobaru giga. Gora gedadi boji n'geki, jidubibu sazabu. 

Gigida gibodo gagaseda gidederiso. Gozesa Grongi-zobu bogo ga bigide gogu ba boza. Zasubaru bagi Rinto zobuzodi ra dushibiga gageda boro goseza. Bonbagi bo Gegeru-ze rodo doro Rinto zogi bugadu gida boropada giza. Riso, bo boshaginbi gududedesu gosebodi didiga. Bobo me gin, bobo zu gaga, bobo jubo zogubo Kuuga za. Gaga, gosebi bosoga se suba, jibeduguzu ba, gaga gadobi resugagigi.
